### Delete Post [DELETE]
Move post into recycle bin

+ Request
    + Header

        Authorization: JWT "JWT_TOKEN_HERE"

+ Response 204 

## Posts Collection [/posts]
### List all posts [GET]
+ Parameters
    + filter (string) - Filter by author / category 
    + id (string) - Author (user_id) / category
    + page (string) 10 posts per page

+ Response (application/json)

    {
        "page": 1,
        "filter_by": "author",
        "posts": [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "category_id": 1,
                "category": "Hello",
                "title": "Lorem Ipsum",
                "author": "Miriam",
                "user_id": 2,
                "updated_at": "2018-03-29 19:58:00",
                "revision_id": 103
            }
            ...
        ]
    }

